OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start across some
OL,6,Fcentral and eastern areas, but the
OL,7,Fcloud will quickly lift for most.
OL,8,FHowever, it will linger near some
OL,9,FNorth Sea coasts. Otherwise, another
OL,10,Fdry and sunny day, feeling very warm
OL,11,Fin the southwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with clear spells for
OL,14,Fmost, however areas of low cloud near
OL,15,Fsome North Sea coasts will expand and
OL,16,Fspread inland overnight. Feeling warm
OL,17,Fin the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
